OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1777626370
OL,3,CThey fled antisemitism, but then found
OL,4,Cit at their doorstep
OL,6,FITV News Reporter Sam Holder spoke to
OL,7,FHolocaust survivors in Golders Green
OL,8,Fin the wake of Wednesday's terror
OL,9,Fattack, in which two Jewish men were
OL,10,Fstabbed. And ITV News Political Editor
OL,11,FRobert Peston gives his analysis of
OL,12,Fthe reaction to the attack.
OL,14,FWords by ITV News Reporter Sam Holder
OL,15,Fand Deputy Content Editor Greg Ockrim
OL,17,FA stone's throw from the Golders Green
OL,18,Fterror attack lies the Jewish Care
OL,19,FHolocaust Survivors' Centre.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
