OL,3,CThey fled antisemitism, but then found
OL,4,Cit at their doorstep
OL,6,F"It's pretty terrifying because it
OL,7,Fmeans that antisemitism, or I prefer
OL,8,Fto say Jew-hatred, is on the rise,"
OL,9,FRuth Barnett, who arrived in the UK on
OL,10,Fthe Kindertransport, told ITV News.
OL,12,FTheir grandchildren and great-
OL,13,Fgrandchildren go to schools that look
OL,14,Fmore like army bases or prisons.
OL,16,FEach morning, parents watch their
OL,17,Fchildren put on their school uniform
OL,18,Fto go to class behind high walls,
OL,19,Fsecure gates, all protected by guards
OL,20,Fwith stab-proof vests.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/9
