OL,3,CThey fled antisemitism, but then found
OL,4,Cit at their doorstep
OL,6,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,7,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,8,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,9,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,11,FOn Thursday morning, sixth form pupils
OL,12,Ffrom Yavneh College were preparing
OL,13,Fballoon arches, writing thank you
OL,14,Fcards to teachers, making future
OL,15,Funiversity and apprenticeship plans as
OL,16,Fthe hours counted down to walking out
OL,17,Fthe school gates for the last time
OL,18,Fbefore their A-level exams.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/9
