OL,3,CThey fled antisemitism, but then found
OL,4,Cit at their doorstep
OL,6,FIt's a British comprehensive school
OL,7,Fthat runs drills for what to do if
OL,8,Fthey become a target for an attack,
OL,9,Fbecause the majority of its students
OL,10,Fare Jewish.
OL,12,FThe school spends #175,000 a year on
OL,13,Fsecurity.
OL,15,FAfter the attack in Golders Green on
OL,16,FWednesday, where two people were
OL,17,Fstabbed, they were all told to head
OL,18,Fstraight home after the final bell
OL,19,Frang.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
