OL,3,CThey fled antisemitism, but then found
OL,4,Cit at their doorstep
OL,6,F"It feels increasingly unwelcoming to
OL,7,Fbe Jewish in this country," 18-year-
OL,8,Fold Joshua said.
OL,10,F"I didn't know until fairly recently
OL,11,Fthat non-Jewish schools didn't have
OL,12,Fsecurity all the time. I wasn't aware
OL,13,Fthat it wasn't normal for non-Jewish
OL,14,Fcommunities."
OL,16,FOra, 18, said: "It does make you feel
OL,17,Fthat we walk around with a target on
OL,18,Four backs."
OL,26,@rD@AOUxD@POU
