CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1777626370
OL,3,CThey fled antisemitism, but then found
OL,4,Cit at their doorstep
OL,6,FShe told us she gets nervous hearing
OL,7,Fher friends say her name in public
OL,8,Fbecause it sounds Jewish.
OL,10,FThe stabbings in Golders Green,
OL,11,Ffollowing last year's terror attack at
OL,12,FHeaton Park Synagogue in Manchester,
OL,13,Fas well as recent arsons against
OL,14,Ftargets in the Jewish community, have
OL,15,Fsparked conversations at Jewish
OL,16,Fhouseholds across the country, amongst
OL,17,Fyoung and old, about whether the
OL,18,Fcountry can really keep the community
OL,19,Fsafe.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/9
